Not later than 1 year after the date of enactment of this Act, the Secretary shall establish and maintain an electronic database and, in coordination with other Federal and State agencies, issue reporting requirements to make publicly available the status and progress with respect to compliance with applicable requirements of the
National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 ( 42 U.S.C. 4321 et seq.
) and any other Federal, State, or local approval or action required for a project study for which this section is applicable.

